1
00:00:00,955 --> 00:00:02,605
What's the matter, children?
怎么啦,孩子们?

2
00:00:03,837 --> 00:00:07,361
We're tired... and thirsty, Mum.
我们累了…… 口也渴,妈妈.

3
00:00:08,059 --> 00:00:09,684
Are you all right now?
你们现在好些了吗?

4
00:00:10,696 --> 00:00:12,402
No, we aren't.
不,还没有.

5
00:00:13,172 --> 00:00:16,169
Look! There's an ice cream man.
瞧! 有个卖冰淇淋的.

6
00:00:16,951 --> 00:00:19,083
Two ice creams please.
请拿两份冰淇淋.

7
00:00:20,287 --> 00:00:21,900
Here you are, children.
拿着,孩子们.

8
00:00:22,731 --> 00:00:23,797
Thanks, Mum.
谢谢,妈妈.

9
00:00:25,021 --> 00:00:27,614
These ice creams are nice.
这些冰淇淋真好吃.

10
00:00:28,299 --> 00:00:30,132
Are you all right now?
你们现在好了吗?

11
00:00:30,526 --> 00:00:33,785
Yes, we are, thank you!
是的,现在好了,谢谢您!

